data.description: Under 5 years old and ready for new owners this humble home fits your needs. This 3 bed 2 bath ranch features a lovely kitchen and excellent area. Hidden peacefully in the serene town of White Pine and Whispering Pines subdivision, this one sits near the lake and holds an excellent view of the Mountains. THDA, VA, FHA, no problem, Call now and schedule your private showing!
